data.description: Spectacular One of a Kind Property with Views Over acres of Wooded Land - over 50 Acres!  A playground for Hunting/ATV/Birdwatching and so much more. 35x45 ft Workshop/Garage Complete with Heating and A/C + Plumbing/Archery Range.  The 3BR home has been transformed with new roof/siding/USA Insulation/Updated Kitchen/Bath. Replacement windows/ 12x9 Bonus Room. All new Plumbing and Septic on right side of home. 1st Floor Laundry. 2 pellet stoves. 45 acres are Wooded. Must See!
